#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_text_image
msgid "<b>ABOUT US</b>"
msgstr "<b>OM OS</b>"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_cover
msgid "<font style=\"font-size: 62px;\"><b>— Life on Earth —</b></font>"
msgstr ""

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_title
msgid "Changing the world is possible.<br/> We’ve done it before."
msgstr "Verden kan ændres.<br/> Vi har gjort det før."

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_cover
msgid "Get involved"
msgstr "Vær med"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_three_columns
msgid "Habitat Model"
msgstr "Boligmodel"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"Habitats with a minimum footprint on the planet and a maximum positive "
"impact on the local community."
msgstr ""
"Leveområder med et minimalt fodaftryk på planeten og en maksimal positiv "
"indflydelse på det lokale samfund."

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_banner
msgid "Hello Planet."
msgstr "Hej Planet."

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_call_to_action
msgid "Help us protect and preserve for future generations"
msgstr "Hjælp os med at beskytte og bevare naturen for de kommende generationer"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_call_to_action
msgid "Join us and make the planet a better place."
msgstr "Bliv en del af os, og vær med til at gøre planeten til et bedre sted."

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"Learn how to use organic gardening methods to grow the freshest food in your"
" fruit and vegetable garden."
msgstr ""
"Lær, hvordan du ved hjælp af økologiske dyrkningsmetoder kan dyrke de "
"friskeste fødevarer i din frugt- og grøntsagshave."

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_three_columns
msgid "Organic Garden"
msgstr "Økologisk have"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_cover
msgid ""
"Our mission is to create a shared plan<br/> for saving the planet’s most "
"exceptional wild places."
msgstr ""
"Vores opgave er at udarbejde en fælles plan<br/> for at redde de mest "
"enestående vildmarksområder på vores planet."

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_three_columns
msgid "Read more"
msgstr "Få mere at vide"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_three_columns
msgid "Recycling water"
msgstr "Genanvendelse af vand"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"Recycling water for reuse applications instead of using freshwater supplies "
"can be a water-saving measure."
msgstr ""
"Genanvendelse af vand i stedet for at bruge ferskvand kan være en "
"vandbesparende foranstaltning."

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_text_image
msgid "Shaping our future"
msgstr "At forme vores fremtid"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_color_blocks_2
msgid "Sky is the limit."
msgstr ""

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model:ir.model,name:theme_treehouse.model_theme_utils
msgid "Theme Utils"
msgstr "Designværktøjer"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_text_image
msgid ""
"With all the global problems our planet faces today,<br/> communities of "
"people concerned with them are growing<br/> to prevent the negative impact."
msgstr ""
"I lyset af alle de globale problemer, som vores planet står over for i "
"dag,<br/> vokser de fællesskaber af mennesker, der beskæftiger sig med disse "
"problemer,<br/> for at forhindre de negative konsekvenser."

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_picture
msgid "Working Together"
msgstr "Samarbejde"
